    # "Before class starts, Mrs. McGee walks up to me and hands me a note."
    "Antes da aula começar, a Sra. McGee aproxima-se de mim e entrega-me um bilhete."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:9
translate portuguese counselorchat0_21836b82:

    # et "Mrs. Spann asked me to give this to you."
    et "A Sra. Spann pediu-me para te entregar isto."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:10
translate portuguese counselorchat0_bd30ead8:

    # pc "Mrs. Spann?"
    pc "A Sra. Spann?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:13
translate portuguese counselorchat0_623b860f:

    # "She went back to the front of the class and I sat down in my chair to look at the note."
    "Ela voltou para a frente da sala e eu sentei-me na minha cadeira para ler o bilhete."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:14
translate portuguese counselorchat0_f951836e:

    # "\"[pcname], I hope you are doing well.\""
    "\"[pcname], espero que estejas bem.\""

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:15
translate portuguese counselorchat0_53cbedc0:

    # "\"I wanted to let you know that my office is always open to students in the morning.\""
    "\"Queria que soubesses que o meu gabinete está sempre aberto aos alunos pela manhã.\""

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:16
translate portuguese counselorchat0_920e13be:

    # "\"If you wanted, you could come in and chat about anything on your mind, anything you might need guidance with.\""
    "\"Se quiseres, podes entrar e conversar sobre qualquer coisa que te esteja a preocupar, qualquer coisa em que possas precisar de orientação.\""

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:17
translate portuguese counselorchat0_477638c6:

    # "\"Feel free to come in any time. I'd love to talk with you and help you on your education journey,\""
    "«Sente-se à vontade para entrar a qualquer hora. Adoraria conversar consigo e ajudá-lo na sua jornada educativa,»"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:18
translate portuguese counselorchat0_b2f40073:

    # "\"Or with anything else that might be holding you back from achieving your full potential.\""
    "«Ou com qualquer outra coisa que possa estar a impedi-lo de atingir o seu pleno potencial.»"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:19
translate portuguese counselorchat0_077f0024:

    # "\"Hope to see you soon.\""
    "«Espero vê-lo em breve.»"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:20
translate portuguese counselorchat0_e90ba47d:

    # "\"- Gertrude Spann, Student Counselor, Skyhill College.\""
    "«- Gertrude Spann, Conselheira Académica, Skyhill College.»"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:21
translate portuguese counselorchat0_62e8d668:

    # "Open every morning, huh? Maybe I should go chat with her sometime."
    "Aberto todas as manhãs, é? Talvez devesse ir conversar com ela um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Counselorchat0.rpy:22
translate portuguese counselorchat0_39404337:

    # "I put the note away and focus on my classes, but nothing else interesting happens the rest of the day and then it is time to go to work."
    "Guardo o bilhete e concentro-me nas aulas, mas nada de interessante acontece durante o resto do dia e depois chega a hora de ir trabalhar."

